.TH "tty_termios_hw_change" 9 "tty_termios_hw_change" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
tty_termios_hw_change \- check for setting change
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" tty_termios_hw_change
.BI "(const struct ktermios *a "  ","
.BI "const struct ktermios *b "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "a" 12
termios
.IP "b" 12
termios to compare

Check if any of the bits that affect a dumb device have changed
between the two termios structures, or a speed change is needed.
